{"type": "article", "id": 9574, "title": "如果你拥有三辆车，那该把家设计成这样", "description": "在这个家庭里，车和人共享着一个温暖的空间。", "date": "2015-05-15T08:17:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10129, "name": "房车"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 272, "name": "建筑设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 86, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071423397gcC2OPUilwZ69L8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t近日 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/kikumi-kusumoto-ter-toyota-shi-japan-05-13-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom 网站贴出了一间“车房”</a>。这个小小的房子坐落在日本的爱知县，爱知县以 TOYOTA 的产地而闻名。房子的主人是一位老母亲，家中住着儿子、儿媳以及孩子们。由于家里有三辆车，他们专门请来了<a href=\"http://ks-kusumoto.com/home.php\" target=\"_blank\"> ks 建筑事务所</a>的设计师  kikumi kusumoto 为自己设计房子，第一层的开放空间专门为三辆车而设。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142334IGcjhtlzY2a68To4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>夜景</em> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t窗户的设计考虑到了临近的街道和采光。房子使用的材料主要有木材、砖瓦、混凝土、铁、不锈钢等。照明和家具形成了一个温暖的家庭空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060714233431V9nMfYNqXgOAr5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t房屋的入口处\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071423346e8ArG1Z2EMVOYfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从这个楼梯走上去，是工作区\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142335qKpHbigaefQW85tw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t工作区\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071423367yv9WroO5ClX1wRE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从另一个角度看工作区\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142336Fp03Y1uq7gbeXxOj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t餐厅\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142337S8h1JYV2d0DcyEXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t客厅\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142337r4p5kHehAb9zic3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t厨房\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071423386bQsIz0PYGHpFVLW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t日式的卧室\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607142338Qaown36x0EHgG4Vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t日光\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/kikumi-kusumoto-ter-toyota-shi-japan-05-13-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom网站</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}